post1.caption:
UNBOXING TIME! Calling all breastfeeding moms! 
Kali ini aku mau share breastfeeding essentials dari @lansinohid, 💜

💜 HPA®️ Lanolin Nipple Cream: Helps soothe & protect sore, cracked nipples and dry skin
💜 Disposable Breast Pads : Absorbent, comfortable, leak-proof
💜 Nipple Shield: Helps breastfeeding continue through latch-on difficulties
💜 TheraPearl 3in1 Hot or Cold Breast Therapy: Helps relieve engorged breasts & encourages let down
💜 Breastfeeding Pillow: Enables comfortable feeding sessions for baby and mum
💜 2in1 Electric Breast Pump: Enhanced adjustability and convenience
💜 Breastmilk Storage Bags: Pre-sterilised and leak proof

Lansinoh product sudah available di baby shops atau di official store Lansinoh Indonesia di berbagai marketplace.

post6.caption:
It’s been a month since aku officially jadi new mom. And… being new parents are exciting, but it is not always sunshine and rainbows. 

Breastfeeding itself is an emotionally meaningful yet challenging journey, Salah satunya adalah challenge untuk memberi nutrisi ekstra ke tubuh, since aku juga harus memberikan ASI yang berkualitas untuk Gili. Luckily, I got help from @herbana.id Breastfeeding Support Package Daun Katuk & Daun Kelor. 2 herbal ekstrak ini memiki 100% plant-based ingredients dengan segudang manfaat baik. Also, produk ini cocok juga untuk bayi yang memiliki alergi. ✨

Now, I feel that breastfeeding is become less challenging and more fun 🌸

#Herbana #BreastfeedingSupportPackage #reliefSARIDaunKatuk #reliefSARIDaunKelor

post11.caption:
Having experienced what nature has so abundantly given us, I believe in the importance of taking small, everyday steps to protect and conserve it for us and even the generations after us 🌱 Keywords: small, everyday steps ✨

Dalam kegiatan sehari-hari sampai mengisi dekorasi rumah, aku coba menggunakan dengan produk lokal yang memang aku suka (yes, #MakinLokalMakinSayang), dan bonus poinnya kalau produknya sendiri diproduksi secara eco-friendly, seperti koleksi #SleepBuddyforEarth. Breathing new lives to unused fabric has never felt this homey 🏡 Stay tuned for more, I’ll reveal my favorites from this @sleep.buddy special collection. Soon! #SleepBuddyAlwaysTellStories
